    <item>
      <title>市场招呼德国的投票结果，股票收益，欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/dax-futures-gain-with-euro-in-asia-after-german-vote-outcome</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保守党领导人弗里德里希·梅尔兹（Friedrich Merz）在周日的选举中获胜后，欧元攀升和德国的基准库存量表提高了，这为增加支出的枢纽开辟了道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/dax-futures-gain-with-euro-in-asia-after-german-vote-outcome</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 03:33:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黄金持续记录，因为ETF诱导资金和美元削弱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/gold-holds-near-record-high-as-weak-us-data-spurs-haven-buying</link>
      <description><![CDATA[戈德（Gold）的交易略低于上周的纪录，因为美元兑现了，投资者权衡了以金银支持的交易所资金的持股量，这些资金可以帮助价格挑战每盎司3,000美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/gold-holds-near-record-high-as-weak-us-data-spurs-haven-buying</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 00:16:24 GMT</pubDate>
